data.description: Azure is a cloud computing service for building, testing, deploying, and managing applications and services through Microsoft-managed data centers.

Imperva is a cyber security software and services company for networking, data, and application security.

Azure Monitor collects monitoring telemetry from a variety of on-premises and Azure sources. Azure Monitor helps you maximise the availability and performance of your applications and services.
